Package: squashinformr
Type: Package
Title: A Package for Web Scraping squashinfo.com
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hayden MacDonald [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Hayden MacDonald <hayden.macdonald.8778@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows sports enthusiasts to easily access data related to 
    the Professional Squash Association's World Tour from SquashInfo. The functions within this package
    scrape, parse, and clean data associated with players, tournaments, and rankings data.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0),
         magrittr
Imports: dplyr,
         plyr,
         lubridate,
         stringr,
         tidyr,
         rvest,
         xml2,
         httr,
         purrr,
         polite,
         naniar,
         gtools,
         gsubfn,
         janitor
Suggests: testthat,
          knitr,
          rmarkdown
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/HaydenMacDonald/squashinformr
